node.text:
...are we just giving you this Peanut Butter Cheesecake for the fun of it?

INGREDIENTS
125g plain flour
225g sugar
38g unsweetened cocoa powder
1 tsp baking powder
¾ tsp baking soda
½ tsp salt
½ tsp instant coffee
125ml whole milk
63 ml vegetable oil
1 large egg
1 tsp vanilla extract
125ml boiling water
1 1/2 cups heavy cream
1 1/4 cup creamy peanut butter, not natural
575g cream cheese, softened to room temperature
1 1/4 cup powdered sugar
250ml heavy cream
2 tbsp clear corn syrup
125g milk chocolate finely chopped
100g dark chocolate finely chopped
Finely chopped peanuts and chocolate shavings

node.text:
CHICKEN PARM MAC AND CHEESE

INGREDIENTS
2 chicken breasts
150g plain flour
1 tsp dried Italian seasoning
2 eggs, whisked
140g panko breadcrumbs 
30g grated parmesan cheese
Oil for shallow frying
 
30g butter
30g flour
500ml milk
½ tsp mustard powder
¼ tsp paprika
? ? tsp nutmeg
Salt and pepper to taste
400g cooked macaroni
100g grated mozzarella,
100g grated cheddar
50g grated gruyere
 
250g tomato pasta sauce 
50g grated mozzarella cheese
Fresh basil leaves

CHICKEN PARM SPAGHETTI PIE

INGREDIENTS
* 	2 chicken breasts, butterflied
* 	Salt & pepper, to season
* 	100g flour
* 	4 eggs, beaten
* 	180g panko breadcrumbs
* 	1 ltr vegetable oil, for frying
* 	800g spaghetti
* 	150g parmesan
* 	5 eggs
* 	250ml double cream
* 	1 tbsp salt
* 	1/2 tbsp black pepper
* 	Sliced mozzarella
* 	1 tablespoon olive oil
* 	1 large onion chopped
* 	2 teaspoons minced garlic
* 	400g tomato passata
* 	Salt and pepper to taste
* 	1 teaspoon dried Italian herbs
* 	1 teaspoon sugar

node.text:
SERVES
6 people
INGREDIENTS
Beef Stew:
2 tbsp flour
Salt and pepper
1 lb diced stewing beef
1 tbsp vegetable oil
1 tbsp butter
2 onions, diced small
500g mushrooms, sliced
2 cloves garlic, diced small
2 tbsp flour
1 tbsp tomato paste
2 cups red wine
1 1/2 cups beef stock
1 tsp salt
1 tsp pepper
 
Calzone Dough:
½ cup warm water
.25oz dry yeast
1 tsp yeast
½ cup water
2 tbsp olive oil
2 tbsp honey
¼ tsp salt
3 cups plain flour
 
Grated Cheddar Cheese
 
Garlic Butter:
½ cup salted butter
3 cloves garlic, minced
1 tbsp Chopped parsley
Pepper

node.title: THE GIANT BEEF STEW CHEESY CALZONE - ENOUGH FOR THE WHOLE FAMILY TO ENJOY

node.text:
Boursin, Nduja AND Crab Linguine by the sea?? We're ready!

#linguine  #noleftovers #foodforthought #foodoftheday #summerrecipes

4 easy creamy sausage pasta recipes - comforting, creamy and perfect for sharing!

Tuscan sausage lasagna 
INGREDIENTS
* 	2 tbsp mild olive oil
* 	1 red chilli, finely diced
* 	2 garlic cloves, finely diced
* 	1 red onion, finely chopped
* 	3 mixed peppers
* 	9 Italian sausages, squeezed from their casings
* 	150g mixed tomatoes
* 	2 tbsp plain flour
* 	100ml white wine
* 	200ml chicken stock
* 	200ml whole milk
* 	1 jar sun dried tomatoes, drained
* 	Cooked spinach, 300g
* 	1 tbsp sea salt
* 	1 tbsp pepper
* 	lasagna sheets
* 	200g grated mozzarella
* 	40g grated parmesan

Creamy tomato and sausage pasta bake 
INGREDIENTS
* 	1 onion, chopped
* 	1 garlic, chopped 
* 	100g chestnut mushrooms, finely chopped
* 	6 sausages, meat removed from skins
* 	1 jar of passata
* 	100ml white wine
* 	2 cups of chicken stock
* 	1/2 tsp chilli flakes
* 	1 tsp sugar
* 	50ml double cream
* 	100g parmesan
* 	300g conchiglie pasta shells, cooked
* 	75g grated mozzarella
* 	75g cheddar
* 	75g fresh breadcrumbs
* 	2 tbsp dried rosemary

Cajun chicken sausage pasta

INGREDIENTS
3tablespoons of extra virgin olive oil
2 chicken breasts, cut into bite-sized pieces
14 oz smoked sausage, sliced diagonally
4 cloves of garlic, minced
3 1/2 cups low-sodium chicken broth
2 cups of heavy cream
450g dry penne pasta
2 tbsp of Cajun seasoning plus more for topping
1 cup shredded parmesan cheese
1/4 cup  parsley, finely chopped

Creamy sausage parpadelle
INGREDIENTS
* 	2 tbsp olive oil
* 	1 large brown onion, diced
* 	2 cloves garlic
* 	1 tbsp fennel seeds
* 	8 sausages, squeezed from casings
* 	150ml white wine
* 	1 tsp chilli flakes
* 	300ml chicken stock
* 	1 can chopped tomatoes
* 	2 tbsp tomato puree
* 	3 tbsp double cream
* 	1 tsp black pepper
* 	1 tsp sea salt
* 	30g parmesan, grated
* 	400g parpadelle
* 	200g mozzarella, torn
* 	Handful fresh basil, sliced
 #staplerecipes #mealprep #foodprep #chefmode #pastamaster #pantryorganization #pastarecipe #recipeshare #pantryprep #easyrecipes

4 easy dessert recipes in 60 seconds or less! Save these for a quick and simple sugar fix!

 WHOLE APPLE CARAMEL CAKE
 INGREDIENTS
1/2 cup unsalted butter softened
1/3 cup granulated sugar
1/3 cup packed brown sugar
4 eggs
1 tsp vanilla essence
1 1/3 cups all-purpose flour
1 1/2 teaspoon baking powder
1/2 teaspoon baking soda
1/4 cup milk
 
12 apples, peeled and cored
1 cup brown sugar
4 tbsp unsalted butter
1 tbsp sea salt
1 tbsp vanilla extract
1/2 cup single cream

MUFFIN TIN CINNAMON ROLL PIES
INGREDIENTS
4 pie crusts
4 tsp cinnamon
2 tbsp butter
1 tsp cinnamon
3/4 cup sugar
3 tbsp plain flour
6 apples, peeled, cored and diced
2 tbsp Demerara sugar
Egg wash
Vanilla Ice Cream

GLAZED FRENCH TOAST CINNAMON SWIRL
INGREDIENTS
16 slices white bread, crusts off
3/4 cup softened butter
3/4 cup dark brown sugar
3 tsp cinnamon
3 eggs
1 cup cream
1/4 cup milk
2 tbsp sugar
1 1/2 tsp vanilla
1 cup icing sugar
2 tbsp melted butter
1 tbsp milk

CINNAMON ROLL STAR
INGREDIENTS
* 	1 cup caster sugar
* 	2 tbsp cinnamon
* 	2 sheets puff pastry
* 	2 tbsp melted butter
* 	1 beaten egg
* 	4 oz cream cheese, warmed
* 	1 cup icing sugar
* 	5 tbsp milk
* 	1/2 tsp vanilla essence
